title: Glen Innes to Tamaki Drive urban cycleway begins (Ministry of Transport of New Zealand)
text: ( Source : Ministry of Transport of New Zealand ) Transport Minister Simon Bridges has turned the first sod of a major urban cycleway that will connect Auckland 's eastern suburbs with the city centre. The Glen Innes to Tamaki Drive Shared Path
